criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Male or female patients, between 18 and 50;

          2. Pathology or suspected patellofemoral joint pathology in which a CT examination is
             required for a diagnostic examination;

          3. Signature of informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients incapable of understanding and will;

          2. Pregnant women;

          3. Patients with history of previous fractures of the knee.

          4. BMI> 40.
